Package vaccine_service

Class Date

java.lang.Object
vaccine_service.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
Represents a calender date with three fields: day, month, and year. Can check if date is a valid calendar date.
Author:
nabihah, maryam
